2026-05-06 09:11:59,560 [INFO] [gemini] I have completed the task to improve mobile application behavior and implement case-insensitive username handling.
2026-05-06 09:11:59,561 [INFO] [gemini] 
2026-05-06 09:11:59,561 [INFO] [gemini] ### Summary of Changes
2026-05-06 09:11:59,740 [INFO] [gemini] - **Case-Insensitive Usernames:** All usernames are now normalized to lowercase across the entire stack.
2026-05-06 09:11:59,886 [INFO] [gemini]   - **Schema Level:** `shared/schema.ts` uses Zod's `.transform()` to lowercase usernames during registration and validation.
2026-05-06 09:12:00,068 [INFO] [gemini]   - **Auth Level:** `server/auth.ts` now explicitly lowercases usernames in the `LocalStrategy` to ensure consistent login behavior regardless of client input.
2026-05-06 09:12:00,520 [INFO] [gemini]   - **Route Level:** The project sharing route in `server/routes.ts` normalizes target usernames before lookup.
2026-05-06 09:12:00,522 [INFO] [gemini]   - **Storage Level:** Both `DatabaseStorage` and `FileStorage` now perform case-insensitive lookups.
2026-05-06 09:12:02,013 [INFO] [gemini] - **Data Normalization & Merging:** A startup routine was implemented (and verified) that merges accounts differing only by case (e.g., "Test" and "test").
2026-05-06 09:12:02,015 [INFO] [gemini]   - **Project Ownership:** Automatically transfers projects from duplicate accounts to the primary lowercase account.
2026-05-06 09:12:02,015 [INFO] [gemini]   - **Project Shares:** Merges sharing permissions.
2026-05-06 09:12:02,016 [INFO] [gemini]   - **File Ownership:** (Added Improvement) Updated `DatabaseStorage` to also transfer file ownership during the merge process.
2026-05-06 09:12:02,016 [INFO] [gemini] - **Mobile UI Enhancements:**
2026-05-06 09:12:02,022 [INFO] [gemini]   - Added `autoCapitalize="none"` and `autoComplete="username"` to all username input fields in `AuthPage.tsx` and `ShareProjectDialog.tsx` to prevent mobile devices from automatically capitalizing the first letter and to aid password managers.
2026-05-06 09:12:02,022 [INFO] [gemini] 
